# <type>(<scope>): <description>
#
# Types: feat, fix, refactor, docs, chore, test, perf, ci, style
# Scope: hooks, config, skills, prompts, tools, scripts, state, docs
#
# Examples:
#   feat(skills): add kb-research-strategist Skill
#   fix(hooks): resolve MinGW double-slash path normalization
#   refactor(config): extract hardcoded timeout to timeouts.yaml
#   docs(operations): add troubleshooting guide
#   chore(state): clean up stale loop-state files
#   test(hooks): add 45 behavior_tracker tests
#
# Rules:
#   - Subject line: imperative mood, no period, max 72 chars
#   - Body: explain WHY, not WHAT (the diff shows WHAT)
#   - Footer: reference issue/ADR if applicable
#
# Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
